{"tid":874090,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"越籍裸女遊蕩 嚇煞途人","createTime":"2018-10-24T02:28:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-24T03:37:57.000Z","uid":147522,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"624ccf37232e6c59a4bbfde4fa5c26196a7f6b9d","tid":874090,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T02:28:06.000Z","msg":"【本報訊】網上流傳一段短片，昨日早上一名全身赤裸的中年女子於關閘廣場附近遊蕩，期間不斷滋擾途人，片段所見，有男途人被嚇得不知所措。涉事女子及後徒步行至關閘廣場地下停車場對出行車道時，被巡經的治安警發現，將她制服並送往醫院檢查，事件起因仍有待調查。<br />\n<br />\n治安警表示，事發在昨日早上八時十四分，警員巡經關閘廣場地下停車場對出行車道時，發現有一名女子全身裸露，隨即派遣女警到場協助，及由消防救護員送往山頂醫院接受治療，事件中無人受傷。警方透露，涉事女子年約五十歲、越南籍、持外地僱員身份認別證。"},{"pid":"8ffc988603cc6f173f3bf3e251311aa98549513f","tid":874090,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T02:28:43.000Z","msg":"50歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cc0230f395ad2d317bda64ced14f15e6f35f720","tid":874090,"uid":210707,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T02:29:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">年約五十歲</span><br />\n<br />\n當我無聽過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cb1b9030b7c50de0a46faed37201698cdfde85b","tid":874090,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T02:29:20.000Z","msg":"網上流傳一段短片"},{"pid":"48924825f189c222c2e46a7e9b61f1d8ff216134","tid":874090,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T02:30:10.000Z","msg":"[img]？[/img]"},{"pid":"540025ec447f08dd90bf845f22fec2fe1798e6df","tid":874090,"uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T02:30:36.000Z","msg":"good"},{"pid":"dad37c245a7b42e09db8efe4c8eb0d2c1d7401f8","tid":874090,"uid":4826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T02:32:09.000Z","msg":"講還講唔好貼相"},{"pid":"7a66045459d27f8cb571c1417bc1685f53ba52b0","tid":874090,"uid":161190,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T03:37:57.0